original_title: Duck Down Presents: Making the Video
overview: Get the inside dope on just how Duck Down Records produces its happenin' music videos. Take a super-powered ride (and remember to take notes!) with co-directors Brandon Kraines and Dru Ha as they lead you through the making of Black Moon's "This Goes Out 2 You" and Boot Camp Clik's "Think Back" videos.
title: Duck Down Presents: Making the Video
